rComments: If every professor in the world was like this one, student suicide wouldnt be a problem. This prof exudes spirit in his own special way, and you will love him for it. Hes not a joke of professor at all tho. But he is a softie, hes funny, very charming, deeply knowledgeable, very wise and has a capacity for compassion that is unlike anyone else!
Super funny and did a great job of explaining the basics of the Greek language. Our assignments were very easy to do while the tests required more effort.

He is very nice and really cares if students understand what he is teaching. He makes class fun by joking around with students and seems very happy and supportive. Would love if every professor was like him.
